		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What picture ?
<br />Well, just make sure you did the mods correcly (INCLUDING A17 wich is needed for FF1). Normaly SNROM is no match to rewire. Only CHRROM boards are a bit harder to rewire.

		

